properties.sfomuseum:description: Set of matchbooks issued by United Air Lines promoting The Club Commuter to Chicago; white covers with red and blue double “C” logo and black strike strips:a. white sleeve for matchbooks with text, “The Club Commuter to Chicago”; same on reverse with black text, “The Club Commuter to New York”; “United Air Lines” on edges;b. matchbook with text, “The Club Commuter to Chicago” and airline logotype; cartoon illustration of two stewardesses in aircraft cabin on reverse;c. matchbook with text, “The Club Commuter to Chicago” and airline logotype; cartoon illustration of two men sitting at back of aircraft cabin on reverse;d. matchbook with text, “The Club Commuter to Chicago” and airline logotype; cartoon illustration of man standing in cabin of aircraft on reverse;e. matchbook with text, “The Club Commuter to Chicago” and airline logotype; cartoon illustration of a man talking to two women on reverse.
properties.sfomuseum:dimensions: 2 x 1 1/2 x 1/4 inches (5.1 x 3.8 x .6 cm)
